---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How we collect, use and protect your personal information when you use this website or contact us for football assessment services."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal">
        <p class="legal__intro">
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use and protect your
          personal information when you use this website or contact me for
          football assessment services.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information I Collect</h2>
        <p>I may collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Any information you provide through the contact form</li>
          <li>Video links or files you choose to send for assessment</li>
          <li>Basic website usage data (via standard analytics tools)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How Your Information Is Used</h2>
        <p>Your information is used to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your enquiries</li>
          <li>Provide assessments and consultancy services</li>
          <li>Arrange bookings, calls or follow-up communication</li>
          <li>Improve the website and services</li>
        </ul>
        <p>I do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.</p>

        <h2>3. How Your Information Is Stored</h2>
        <p>
          Your data is stored securely and is only accessible for as long as
          needed to provide the services you requested.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Contact Form Submissions</h2>
        <p>When you send a message using the contact form:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your details are emailed directly to me</li>
          <li>A copy may be stored in the platform's secure system</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website may use cookies for basic functionality and performance
          tracking. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request a copy of your information</li>
          <li>Ask for your information to be corrected or deleted</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally. Any changes will be
          posted on this page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .legal {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal__intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .legal p {
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .legal li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .legal li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
  }
</style>
